{"tid":449831,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"識social 比iq高重要好多","createTime":"2017-10-27T14:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T17:33:04.000Z","uid":36437,"like":441,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"a5799e078cfa88e99ea1edf8ba646a474baf93ac","tid":449831,"uid":36437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:14:00.000Z","msg":"返工後發現識吹水大過識做野<br />\n<br />\n做得幾好幾快都無用，唔識表達，就以為你唔識<br />\n好多天才，唔識social 最後都係無好結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n世界最緊要就係識包裝識吹水。<br />\n好灰"},{"pid":"98efbda2a1d5733de7c21d114fc9def62d20c530","tid":449831,"uid":138594,"like":36,"dislike":6,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:17:11.000Z","msg":"如果唔係咁 世界仔點上位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57c04cbb45907ed82ea5ed642f1c842f76d5670","tid":449831,"uid":71315,"like":256,"dislike":4,"score":252,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:29:05.000Z","msg":"有父幹 比識 social 有用<br />\n<br />\nsocial 都係靠痴，<br />\n<br />\n有父幹就係人地痴埋黎唔係你痴埋去，<br />\n<br />\nsocial 多數要俾人著數益下人先，<br />\n<br />\n有父幹就食撚晒你班 social 狗d 著數，<br />\n<br />\n然後再一腳踢開你，<br />\n<br />\n反正父幹乜撚都唔怕"},{"pid":"d10adbbcbf2feafd99113ba67496cc847ac8c3ff","tid":449831,"uid":36437,"like":3,"dislike":21,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有父幹 比識 social 有用<br />\n<br />\nsocial 都係靠痴，<br />\n<br />\n有父幹就係人地痴埋黎唔係你痴埋去，<br />\n<br />\nsocial 多數要俾人著數益下人先，<br />\n<br />\n有父幹就食撚晒你班 social 狗d 著數，<br />\n<br />\n然後再一腳踢開你，<br />\n<br />\n反正父幹乜撚都唔怕</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上一代咪又係要識social先上到位"},{"pid":"ddbdb702af748f88ca1bbf10c7597c87edddeb44","tid":449831,"uid":36437,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果唔係咁 世界仔點上位？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，好唔公平<br />\n就算有人知你係做得野，<br />\n明知我識做，都唔交比我做<br />\n因為唔識social<br />\n啲垃圾識得個少少野又份哂野<br />\n明明係我教條友佢又爭住認叻<br />